Rurik d'Kundarak is an adventurer and heir of House [[Kundarak]] and wields a powerful [[Mark of Warding]] that spreads across his entire torso. This variety of [[dragonmark]], known as a "Siberys mark," is mighty, unpredictable, and rare, and the [[dragonmarked house]] keeps a careful eye on him. See <<navAndScrollToHeader "dragonmark" "Siberys Dragonmarks">> for more information.